- We have learned that the grievences reported across the student cohort are largely consistent and limited in scope, suggesting that a focused technological solution targeting as mall number of well defined issues would address the majority of students grievences. The scope of the MVP was limited to EAIT students to ensure feasibility of development within the available timeline and to maintain a standard of product quality corresponding with a more narrowly defined target cohort.
